Father Roder has been the priest for 8 years, a lot has happened of events. the very beautiful celebrations and in particular for events special events were highlighted by the Schola led by the Maitre de Chapelle Pierre Isabellon, and the organist. Father Roder took very good care of the young people, there was non-stop patronage, catechism, pilgrimages and spiritual evenings were organized. The Parish Festival Les Follies de Saint Georges twice a year was a success, also at the end of the year Saint Nicolas. He leaves his children who have always followed him, but who will not be forgotten and hopes that they will continue to do what they have started. Father Roder took initiatives in the right direction, he leaves a Parish full of life. I wish good luck to the new priest who will need the support of the Parishioners, and hopes that it will remain in the continuity of what has been undertaken and that the good atmosphere will continue  Patrick Bathelier
